Patch: %n.patch

ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man --disable-dependency-tracking --disable-schemas-install PKG_CONFIG_PATH="%p/lib/pango-ft219/lib/pkgconfig:%p/lib/fontconfig2/lib/pkgconfig:%p/lib/freetype219/lib/pkgconfig:$PKG_CONFIG_PATH" FREETYPE_CONFIG=%p/lib/freetype219/bin/freetype-config

